        Role Details:
        Digital Content Ratings provides clients with a view of what content people view on computers, smartphones, tablets, and other digital devices. This position will focus on the weighting methodology for panel data that flow into Digital Content Ratings. The goal is to reduce bias and variance by enhancing the current weighting methodology.
        Responsibilities
        * Understand the challenges underlying digital measurement
        * Conduct research on methodology enhancements using non-traditional weighting techniques
        * Write and validate methodology
        * Work with software engineers to implement production changes
        * Work with product team on responding to-day-to day measurement inquiries
